# Porting from construction-management

## Path remap

| CM (source) | construction-sql |
|---|---|
| `pages/` | `app/pages/` |
| `components/PurchaseOrders/` | `app/components/purchaseOrders/` |
| `components/ChangeOrders/` | `app/components/changeOrders/` |
| `components/Payables/` | `app/components/payables/` |
| `components/Shared/` | `app/components/shared/` |
| `components/Reports/` | `app/components/Reports/` |
| `utils/` | `app/utils/` |
| `composables/` | `app/composables/` |
| `stores/` | `app/stores/` |

## Rules

1. **Merge diffs** into existing files — do not blind-overwrite ported modules
2. **Supabase → Prisma:** replace `.from().select()` with Prisma queries; keep business logic identical
3. **Storage:** use data URLs / JSON in MSSQL columns (no Supabase buckets)
4. **Port tests** alongside features under `test/unit/`
5. **Skip:** `server/api/webhooks/*`, entity-usage-sync, Supabase auth/users
